high_descs: Turn right and walk to the long stand that is along the wall across the room
Pick up the spray bottle that is closest to the wall.
Turn around and cross the room then turn left to face the side of the toilet
Place the spray bottle on the back of the toilet
Turn around and cross the room then turn right and walk to the long stand along the wall, the stand that is on the left
Pick up the yellow spray bottle.
Turn around and walk to the long stand and then turn left and walk across the room then turn left to face the side of the toilet
Place the spray bottle on the back to the toilet to the left of the other spray bottle
anns.task_desc: Place spray bottles on the back of a toilet

high_descs: Turn right and go to the cabinet by the sink.
Pick up a spray bottle on the cabinet.
Turn around and go to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle on the toilet.
Turn around and go to the cabinet by the door.
Pick up a spray bottle on the cabinet.
Turn around and go to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles to the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around in the bathroom
Walk over to the counter
Grab the yellow spray bottle and walk it over to the toilet
Put the yellow spray bottle on the back of the toilet
turn around and go back to the counter
look at the other spray bottle
Pick that spray bottle up and carry it to the toilet
Place that spray bottle on the back of the toilet with the other one
Head to your right until you are standing directly in front of two yellow bottles
Pick up a yellow bottle off of the counter
Turn around and walk towards the toilet, then face left
Place the yellow bottle on top of the toilet
Turn around and then head to your right
Pick up a yellow bottle off of the counter
Return to where you were standing facing the toilet
Place the second yellow bottle on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Place two yellow bottles on top of a toilet

high_descs: Turn to your right until you are facing the two yellow bottles
Pick up a yellow bottle off of the side counter
Head backwards and then face the toilet on your left
Put a yellow bottle on top of the toilet tank
Turn to your left and when you reach the wall, turn to your right and approach the other side counter
Pick up a yellow bottle off of the side counter
Head back to the right side of the toilet
Put the other yellow bottle on top of the toilet tank
anns.task_desc: Put two yellow bottles on top of the toilet
